	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Another proposal: iNES+JSON. 
<br />
<br />iNES compatible header (16 bytes)
<br />optional PRG RAM preload pattern (512 bytes)
<br />PRG ROM data (16384*p bytes)
<br />CHR ROM data (8192*c bytes)
<br />new header, in JSON format (??? bytes)
<br />
<br />This preserves the IPS patchability and the compatibility with old emulators.
<br />
<br />The new header might look like this:
<br />{"board":"SNROM","prg-ram":8192,"prg-ram-battery":true}

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


