		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is the goal to maintain backward compatibility with iNES? Because a couple of utilities don't seem to tolerate junk on the end (including ones I wrote).
<br />
<br />I'm not sure I'd like to parse anything beyond trivial JSON inside one of those  trivial nes-on-a-chip or cheap NES playing cellphones. 
<br />
<br />Is gif/png style tagged format such a terrible thing? 4 character codes with a length for each chunk seems pretty easy to me. for attributes like board, mapper, features, etc as long as everyone can agree on a fourCC you're gold.
<br />
<br />anyone has any links to status/info/draft on an ines2?

		

		</td>
